snippet.title: Best VGM 543 - Breath of Fire - Forest
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 204 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ztiSivmoE0c
Best VGM 1335 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KULCV3TgyQk

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Breath of Fire (1994)
Forest
Yoko Shimomura, Yasuaki "Bun Bun" Fujita, Mari Yamaguchi, Minae Fuji
